{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":760,"text":"I'm often asked"},{"time":2680,"text":"why I do art,"},{"time":5000,"text":"what do I want to say\nwith my art photography,"},{"time":7960,"text":"and what is the use of it?"},{"time":10360,"text":"Once in a while I start to worry"},{"time":13040,"text":"how to actually measure\nthe impact from the art"},{"time":17720,"text":"like we do with medicine or technology,"},{"time":21040,"text":"where we can see the results\nand calculate it."},{"time":24760,"text":"Then I would finally be able\nto explain to my mother my art"},{"time":29640,"text":"with real numbers."},{"time":32080,"text":"But my art is so far from metrics,"},{"time":35440,"text":"and moreover, my photography\nis widely exposing the theme of escapism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42640,"text":"My theory is that all of us"},{"time":45800,"text":"struggle sometimes to escape"},{"time":48680,"text":"in order to analyze our reality,"},{"time":51480,"text":"appreciate it or change."},{"time":54800,"text":"I don't work with daily life as it is,"},{"time":57920,"text":"and I'm not a documentary photographer"},{"time":61280,"text":"in the common sense."},{"time":63600,"text":"But I am a documentary photographer"},{"time":66640,"text":"in a different sense."},{"time":68360,"text":"I document dreams."},{"time":71600,"text":"I work with daily life as it could be,"},{"time":74160,"text":"as I imagine it."},{"time":76200,"text":"I am a daydreamer, but at the same time\nI love things that are authentic"},{"time":82360,"text":"and deal with our innermost nature,"},{"time":85800,"text":"which I would never want to escape from."},{"time":88920,"text":"I adore complicated personalities,"},{"time":91560,"text":"and real life inspires me\nto create my images."},{"time":96480,"text":"Real life inspires our escape,"},{"time":100200,"text":"and sometimes that escape is very needed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":105240,"text":"I believe heroes are not created easily,"},{"time":109120,"text":"and I choose to work with individuals"},{"time":111720,"text":"who are survivors"},{"time":113680,"text":"and facing everyday routines"},{"time":116160,"text":"that are not always full of color,"},{"time":119040,"text":"people who are on their way\nto a better life,"},{"time":122440,"text":"fighting against life circumstances."}]},{"cues":[{"time":126720,"text":"Why do I choose people\nlike that for my models?"},{"time":129919,"text":"Because I've been in that position myself,"},{"time":132600,"text":"when I had to learn\nhow to survive in real life."},{"time":136840,"text":"I was a student living abroad in London."},{"time":140000,"text":"I was working at two places\nat the same time as a waitress."},{"time":144480,"text":"Obviously that wasn't my dream job,"},{"time":147520,"text":"but I decided to play a game"},{"time":150360,"text":"where I imagined\nthat I am taking a role in a film,"},{"time":155000,"text":"and in the film I am a waitress,"},{"time":158120,"text":"and I need to act great."},{"time":160520,"text":"I used to dye my hair\nand brows to gingerette,"},{"time":164720,"text":"I changed my hair to curly perm,"},{"time":167280,"text":"I lost weight"},{"time":168640,"text":"and made myself believe"},{"time":171160,"text":"I am just a character acting in a film."},{"time":175280,"text":"That isn't forever,"},{"time":176560,"text":"that is all just temporary."},{"time":179400,"text":"That helped me a lot."},{"time":180840,"text":"It motivated me to change my life"},{"time":183520,"text":"and take a hard time as a game."},{"time":187240,"text":"Now, as an artist,"},{"time":189960,"text":"I am creating different\nlives for my models"},{"time":192880,"text":"in order to give them the experience\nof being someone else in reality."},{"time":198360,"text":"Through the photographic process,"},{"time":200640,"text":"all of my models\nbecome like silent movie actors."},{"time":204960,"text":"They are captured at the moment"},{"time":206880,"text":"when they believe\nin being someone else entirely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":211280,"text":"In order to create\na new reality in its entirety,"},{"time":214840,"text":"I physically create\nevery single thing in my work,"},{"time":218760,"text":"sometimes from outfits to the stage."},{"time":221760,"text":"Because I work with analogues,"},{"time":223600,"text":"and I don't make any digital\nmanipulations to my photographs,"},{"time":227720,"text":"I need everything\nto take place in reality,"},{"time":231720,"text":"in spite of the fact that nowadays,"},{"time":234040,"text":"digitally, you can create\npretty much everything."},{"time":238400,"text":"I don't like this path."},{"time":240280,"text":"Even if that reaches perfection,"},{"time":242560,"text":"I see the beauty\nin authenticity of making,"},{"time":246360,"text":"and that's impossible without flaws."},{"time":249880,"text":"A digitally manipulated photograph"},{"time":252320,"text":"is not true for me."},{"time":254000,"text":"It doesn't capture anything real."},{"time":256720,"text":"It's not experienced, not motivating."},{"time":260480,"text":"It's like, instead of going traveling,"},{"time":262840,"text":"you look at someone else's\ntravel photographs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267000,"text":"What I find so exciting"},{"time":269240,"text":"is the ability to make people's dreams\nof being someone else a reality."},{"time":275720,"text":"That's like a drug"},{"time":277320,"text":"which pushes me to keep working,"},{"time":279520,"text":"even without metrics."}]},{"cues":[{"time":283120,"text":"One of my models"},{"time":285040,"text":"had always dreamed\nof being seen as a warrior,"},{"time":289320,"text":"but she wasn't able to do sports\nbecause of her health problems."},{"time":294120,"text":"Half a year ago, she passed away"},{"time":296320,"text":"from heart disease at the age of 22."},{"time":301160,"text":"But two days before her death,"},{"time":303280,"text":"the images we spent months\nworking on together"},{"time":307600,"text":"of her as a warrior\nshe dreamed of becoming"},{"time":311760,"text":"were published at a large exhibition\nin Milan by Vogue Magazine."},{"time":317600,"text":"All her life was about overcoming."},{"time":321800,"text":"Before she died, she had known"},{"time":323840,"text":"that thousands of people\nsaw her image from the land of escapism"},{"time":329000,"text":"and believed in her\nas a brave and fearless warrior."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335560,"text":"For my work, I invite people\nto play a game"},{"time":339200,"text":"like we all used to as children"},{"time":341880,"text":"when we pretend to be someone else"},{"time":343960,"text":"and that process made us really happy."},{"time":347520,"text":"To my mind it is important for grown-ups."},{"time":351720,"text":"We need these transformations"},{"time":353800,"text":"to enact this in the name of art."},{"time":356880,"text":"It gives us the very real feeling\nof being important and powerful"},{"time":362360,"text":"in order to influence our reality."},{"time":366200,"text":"I know this from\nmy own personal experience."},{"time":370080,"text":"I have had so many versions of myself"},{"time":373640,"text":"through my self-portraits"},{"time":375760,"text":"that I've been many different characters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":381040,"text":"Being someone else in the land of escapism"},{"time":384920,"text":"doesn't exactly give us numbers\nthat we can gauge,"},{"time":389000,"text":"but it's like a real lost form of magic"},{"time":392680,"text":"which exists but can't be measured."},{"time":395800,"text":"There is a unique power in art"},{"time":398360,"text":"to transform and lift our limits."},{"time":402000,"text":"Art creates what I call a conjured life,"},{"time":405640,"text":"which helps our existence"},{"time":408240,"text":"and pushes, motivates\nand inspires us to dwell"},{"time":412800,"text":"and express ourselves"},{"time":415360,"text":"without metrics or calculations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":418480,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":419720,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}